title: [Thanatoph, Dead-end]
description: The trail turns into the mountain, winding through a narrow trail edged with tall cliffs to either side.  Finally, it dead-ends at a rough jumble of stones.  Small enclaves and crevices cultivate deep shadows as the cold sun fights its way past the towering rock.
